Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}嗚呼　命の灯を掲げ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 欺いて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.98,0:02:15.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.16,0:02:23.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}ねぇ　無防備だね　美しい戯れに　人は壊れてゆく
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}可笑しいわね
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.17,0:02:39.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}そう　このまま　壊れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:41.91,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}can not, can not, not, not, not deny 紛れもなく真実
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}さあ　預けて　回帰するように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:52.51,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}エネルギーはサイクル　そう　いまは無重力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:59.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}象徴的なパレード　この月夜に仰げよ仰げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord5}‘completeness’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}可笑しいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:39.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H431FAF&\1a&HFF&\bord3}そう　このまま　壊れて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.40,0:01:31.57,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}命運玩弄之下 無聲之音橫流
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}你已捨棄一切名義 只剩模糊殘像哭泣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.95,0:01:41.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,無法 無法否認 毫無疑問的真實
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,交給我吧 從此走向回歸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.79,0:01:52.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,能量不斷循環 重力已經消失
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.51,0:01:59.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,代表性的遊行 於月夜之下祈求
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,「完美無缺」
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.27,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}高舉生命燈火
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.98,OP_CH,,0,0,15,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr6N U-KL\fs60}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., {\fnFZYaSong-H-GBK\fs52}欺騙一切
